<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6181&amp;p=58522#p58522</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6181&amp;p=58522#p58522"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Help! Specific questions on scrolling, nametables, mirroring]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6181&amp;p=58522#p58522"><![CDATA[
I just made a diagram to show what I meant above with scrolling glitches. This is how to minimize the glitches horizontally and vertically - most games did do it in a less optimal way, and as a consequence show much more glitches.<br />Tell me if this is worth putting in the wiki, and if so where.<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Legend :<br />a,b = group of 2 tiles sharing the same color that scrolls out of the visible area<br />c,d = group of 2 tiles sharing the same color that scrolls in visible area<br />--- = pixels from other tiles that always in the visible area &#40;and always show correctly&#41;<br />XXX = pixels which are hidden thanks to the left-clip hardare feature<br />Fine scroll : Low 4 bits of H/V scrolling values. <br />Wrong tile : the tile from the other side of the screen is visible &#40;255 / 256 probability that it's the wrong tile&#41;<br />Wrong color : the good tile is visible, but uses color from the tile of the other side of the screen &#40;3/4 probabilty it's the wrong color&#41;<br /><br />                  Bottom Pixels       Top Pixels        VRAM Updates           Wrong Tile  Wrong colors<br />Fine V Scroll     224..........239    0.............15<br />$00               aaaaaaaabbbbbbbb    ----------------<br />$01               -aaaaaaaabbbbbbb    b---------------                          1 on top<br />$02               --aaaaaaaabbbbbb    bb--------------                          2 on top<br />$03               ---aaaaaaaabbbbb    bbb-------------                          3 on top<br />$04               ----aaaaaaaadddd    dddd------------  d tile row              4 on bottom  4 on top<br />$05               -----aaaaaaaaddd    ddddd-----------                          3 on bottom  5 on top<br />$06               ------aaaaaaaadd    dddddd----------                          2 on bottom  6 on top<br />$07               -------aaaaaaaad    ddddddd---------                          1 on bottom  7 on top<br />$08               --------aaaaaaaa    dddddddd--------  cd attribute row                     8 on bottom<br />$09               ---------aaaaaaa    adddddddd-------                          1 on top     7 on bottom<br />$0a               ----------aaaaaa    aadddddddd------                          2 on top     6 on bottom<br />$0b               -----------aaaaa    aaadddddddd-----                          3 on top     5 on bottom<br />$0c               ------------cccc    ccccdddddddd----  c tile row              4 on bottom<br />$0d               -------------ccc    cccccdddddddd---                          3 on bottom<br />$0e               --------------cc    ccccccdddddddd--                          2 on bottom<br />$0f               ---------------c    cccccccdddddddd-                          1 on bottom<br />$10               ----------------    ccccccccdddddddd   ---&gt; back to $00<br /><br />Overall:<br />Average wrong tile : 0.75 top, 1.25 bottom<br />Average wrong pixel &#40;= wrong color + wrong tile&#41; : 2.125 top, 2.87 bottom<br /><br />                  Right Pixels        Left Pixels       VRAM Updates            Wrong Colors<br />Fine H Scroll     240..........255    XXXXXXXX8......15<br />$00               aaaaaaaabbbbbbbb    ----------------<br />$01               -aaaaaaaabbbbbbb    b---------------<br />$02               --aaaaaaaabbbbbb    bb--------------<br />$03               ---aaaaaaaabbbbb    bbb-------------<br />$04               ----aaaaaaaabbbb    bbbb------------<br />$05               -----aaaaaaaabbb    bbbbb-----------<br />$06               ------aaaaaaaabb    bbbbbb----------<br />$07               -------aaaaaaaab    bbbbbbb---------<br />$08               --------aaaaaaaa    dddddddd--------  d tile column<br />$09               ---------aaaaaaa    adddddddd-------                          1 on left<br />$0a               ----------aaaaaa    aadddddddd------                          2 on left<br />$0b               -----------aaaaa    aaadddddddd-----                          3 on left<br />$0c               ------------aaaa    aaaadddddddd----  cd attribute column     4 on right<br />$0d               -------------aaa    aaaaadddddddd---                          3 on right<br />$0e               --------------aa    aaaaaadddddddd--                          2 on right<br />$0f               ---------------a    aaaaaaadddddddd-                          1 on right<br />$10               ----------------    ccccccccdddddddd  c tile column   -----&gt; back to $00<br /><br />Overall :<br />Average wrong tile : 0<br />Average wrong color : 0.375 left, 0.625 right</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Wed Mar 17, 2010 10:57 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
